Evaluation of Indexing and a Technique for Formalized Search RequestStatement.AFrants, Yu. I.Voiskunskii, V. G.Mukosei, V. I.Kozhina, T. G.
   A method for evaluation of indexing is expounded.  The feasibility is examined of using marked documents instead of requests, called the "beaconmethod".. A M-algorithm for formalized statement of search requests is described and exemplified by an information retrieval system in the nitrogenindustry..